  "flags": {},
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 3rd level, you can exude small tendrils of ectoplasm that can be used to make melee <em>touch</em> attacks as part of a spell with a range of touch. You can make melee <em>touch</em> attacks as if you had an additional 5 feet of reach. You must have a free hand with which to direct the ectoplasm.</p>\n<p>This ability does not otherwise increase your <em>threatened</em> area. At 11th level, this additional reach increases to 10 feet. At 17th level, this additional reach increases to 15 feet.</p>"
    },
